data.description: Welcome home to this corner unit condo located in the desirable 55+ neighborhood of Pines of Delray North in the heart of Delray Beach. This villa style home features 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a Florida room with an extra outdoor patio space with canal views - making it a perfect oasis. New roof, tile floors, and a spacious floor plan - what more could you ask for. Just minutes away from shopping and dining at coastal Atlantic Avenue as well as beautiful beaches. Enjoy the 2 Community Pools, Tennis & Pickle ball courts, Fitness Center, 2 Clubhouses and more! HOA Includes: Amenities, Guard gate/Security, Water, Cable TV. Please note some photos are virtually staged
